HEADWORD: Centimetre
<hw>Cen"ti*me`tre</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>centim⟦egrave⟧tre</ets>;
<ets>centi-</ets> (L. <ets>centum</ets>) + <ets>m⟦egrave⟧tre</ets>. See
<er>Meter</er>.]</ety> <def>The hundredth part of a meter; a measure of
